formatDescription: Stata is a research data analysis and statistical software package. The DTA format contains the Stata dataset.  DTA version 113 is known to be associated with Stata software version 8. Please contact the PRONOM team if you can provide further information about this format.
provenanceCompoundName: Digital Preservation Department / The National Archives
